					<description><![CDATA[I&#039;m amazed by how simple it is to create a map with these instructions. I&#039;d made a query showing paved main roads on Overpass before (http://overpass-turbo.eu/s/7q8), and it took me minutes to turn it into a nice umap. Unfortunately, it seems to be a bit too heavy on either umap, overpass or my bad internet connection. It would be nice to be able to cache this data (which is a lot of course) to a umap server and just have it update itself from time to time.]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I&#8217;m amazed by how simple it is to create a map with these instructions. I&#8217;d made a query showing paved main roads on Overpass before (<a href="http://overpass-turbo.eu/s/7q8" rel="nofollow ugc">http://overpass-turbo.eu/s/7q8</a>), and it took me minutes to turn it into a nice umap. Unfortunately, it seems to be a bit too heavy on either umap, overpass or my bad internet connection. It would be nice to be able to cache this data (which is a lot of course) to a umap server and just have it update itself from time to time.</p>
